    "In the absence of Clue, there is a remarkable decrease in F1 score for both subtasks (-9.51% on Tri-ID and -9.84% on Tri-CLS).",
    "This indicates the significance of our Clues, especially when dealing with events in certain specific domains.",
    "(2) Without descriptions of similar types as context, our method shows a noticeable decrease in performance on the CASIE dataset.",
    "This indicates that descriptions of similar types as context can provide substantial assistance on sentence-level ED, including events in specific domains.",
